### ============================================
### 校园二手交易平台 - 完整测试案例
### ============================================

### 0. 注册买家账号
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "buyer001",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试买家",
  "email": "buyer@test.com",
  "phone": "13800000001"
}

### 1. 注册卖家账号
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "seller001",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试卖家",
  "email": "seller@test.com",
  "phone": "13800000002"
}

### ============================================
### 卖家操作流程
### ============================================

### 2. 卖家登录
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=seller001&password=123456

### 3. 卖家发布商品（需要先手动在数据库插入一个商品，或使用现有商品）
# 注意：如果 /api/articles/create 接口存在，可以使用以下请求
# POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles/create
# Content-Type: application/json
# 
# {
#   "title": "测试商品-二手手机",
#   "description": "九成新iPhone 12，功能完好",
#   "price": 3999.00,
#   "categoryId": 1,
#   "images": "/uploads/test.jpg"
# }

### 4. 查看卖家发布的商品
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/my

### ============================================
### 买家操作流程
### ============================================

### 5. 买家登录
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=buyer001&password=123456

### 6. 浏览商品列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10

### 7. 查看商品详情（假设商品ID=1）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/articles/1

### 8. 创建订单（购买商品ID=1）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/create?articleId=1&quantity=1&address=武汉市洪山区南湖大道&remark=请尽快发货

### 9. 获取我的订单（买家视角）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/my

### 10. 获取订单详情（使用上一步返回的实际订单ID替换下面的1）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1

### ============================================
### 卖家处理订单流程
### ============================================

### 11. 卖家重新登录（如果Session过期）
# 注意：订单ID=1的卖家是ksbird，不是seller001！
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=ksbird&password=123456

### 12. 查看卖家的订单
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/seller

### 13. 卖家发货（使用实际的订单ID替换下面的1）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/ship

### ============================================
### 买家确认收货流程
### ============================================

### 14. 买家重新登录（如果Session过期）
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=buyer001&password=123456

### 15. 确认收货（使用实际的订单ID替换下面的1）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/confirm

### 16. 评价订单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "articleId": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "content": "商品很好，非常满意！卖家发货速度快，包装仔细。"
}

### 17. 查看订单评价
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/review

### ============================================
### 其他测试场景
### ============================================

### 18. 取消订单（在卖家发货前，使用实际订单ID）
# POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/cancel?reason=不想要了

### 19. 测试错误场景 - 未登录访问受保护接口
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/my

### 20. 测试错误场景 - 无权操作他人订单
# 先用买家登录创建一个订单，然后用卖家账号尝试取消该订单
# POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/cancel?reason=测试权限

### ============================================
### 数据清理（可选）
### ============================================

### 21. 退出登录
POST http://localhost:8080/logout
